   <p>H<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">d</hi></hi> Q<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">rs</hi></hi> 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Ky Cav
<lb/>Near <placeName ref="cwgk:P00005238">Powder Springs Ga
</placeName><lb/><date when="1864-06-27">June 27" 1864</date>,
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N001000">Gov Bramlette</persName><lb/>Sir</p>
<p>I have the honor to recommend to you for Promotion Major <persName ref="cwgk:N00005142">F. M Helveti </persName>to the rank of Lt Colonel vice <persName ref="cwgk:N00005138">Adams</persName> promoted also Capt <persName ref="cwgk:N00005151">A. T. Keen</persName> to the rank of Major vice Helveti promoted.</p>
<p>I am very Resptly
<lb/>your ob<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">t</hi></hi> Serv<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">t</hi></hi>
<lb/>S Adams Col 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Ky Cav</p>
<p><figure type="hr"/><note place="left margin">1.2.3.4.5</note>Maj F^rancis^ M Helviti com Lieut Col. 1 Cavy <date when="1864-06-27">June 27/64</date> vice S. Adams promoted,<figure type="hr"/>
<lb/><note place="left margin">1.2.3.4.5.</note>Capt. Anderson S. Keene com Maj 1 Cavy <date when="1864-06-27">June 27/64</date> vice F. M. Helviti promd.<pb/></p>
<p><hi rend="underline">1 Cavy</hi>
<lb/>Head Qrs. 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Ky Cavy 
<lb/>nr. Powder Springs
<lb/><date when="1864-06-27">June 27. 1864</date><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Adams Silias Colonel<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Recommends Maj F. M Helviti for promotion to Lieut Col and Capt. A. T. Keen to the rank of Major.<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Com issd &amp; fow<hi rend="sup">d</hi> <date when="1864-07-09">July 9. 1864</date><figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Rec<hi rend="sup">d</hi> A. G. O. <date when="1864-07-09">July 9. 1864</date></p>
